title: My Name Is Not Alice
description: Librarian's Note: Alternate-cover edition for ASIN B015CNYJB0Alice is a high school princess. Blonde. Beautiful. Shallow. Until she meets a little white rabbit, and her world turns upside down. The line between reality and fantasy blurs, then vanishes altogether. And Alice becomes a girl who attracts Trouble. Trouble with a capital T.
author: Angelika Rust
